{"tid":1640850,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"諗到個平唱美金方法...","createTime":"2019-10-09T06:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-10T05:00:41.000Z","uid":5178,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"1888f54ef25e07d6a6ea25b5944ab38d6f43824b","tid":1640850,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"買今買入5號仔, 聽日放<br />\n每手有40蚊USD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828f056c84e86a55d4711151a1e2da624b5414b1","tid":1640850,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:50:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4139d41808b1bc9aaa2a28d375de3b9f65cc425","tid":1640850,"uid":20820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:52:46.000Z","msg":"IB VS FT VS CS VS TD 邊個好D?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1436793\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1436793</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f3b2aa28889d4d464694717e2f2bd04cc2581dd","tid":1640850,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:53:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbbd4abfc966318a44006923ad242d4490e2b142","tid":1640850,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:53:13.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"d3a8c196ba893cd39bb273df767bfc86b1518fa8","tid":1640850,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:53:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a5f01658d61f0484fd46da9d74bf58eace87a92","tid":1640850,"uid":313764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:54:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hLCPmok.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhLCPmok.jpg&h=d80cc8eb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日話要爭取國際線支持，我依家開左個英文版連儂牆啦，全部同我入去瘋狂貼文宣!<br />\n<br />\n[English] LIHKG Lennon Wall ver 1.0<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1640768\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1640768</a>"},{"pid":"f82484684da433fa318b32d5a703743c627c29ee","tid":1640850,"uid":193290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1888f54ef25e07d6a6ea25b5944ab38d6f43824b","tid":1640850,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T06:50:12.000Z","msg":"買今買入5號仔, 聽日放<br />\n每手有40蚊USD<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T05:00:41.000Z","msg":"股價會扣番"}]}